trans-unit.source: Delegate used by the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> class for deserialization of SOAP-encoded XML data types that map to collections or enumerations.
trans-unit.target: Representanten brukes av den <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>klasse deserialisering av SOAP-kodede data datatyper som tilordnes samlinger eller nummereringer.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>

trans-unit.source: During initialization, the .NET Framework XML serialization infrastructure dynamically generates and compiles a temporary class for deserialization derived from the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializationReader> class.
trans-unit.target: Under initialisering av .NET Framework XML-serialisering dynamisk genererer og kompilerer en midlertidig klasse deserialisering avledet fra <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializationReader>klassen.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializationReader>

trans-unit.source: During this process, the .NET Framework generates collection fix-up methods that use the XmlSerializationCollectionFixupCallback delegate.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework genererer samlingen rett opp metoder som bruker XmlSerializationCollectionFixupCallback representanten under denne prosessen.

trans-unit.source: This occurs for SOAP-encoded arrays or SOAP-encoded, multi-reference elements whose data types, in either case, map to .NET Framework collections or enumerations.
trans-unit.target: Dette skjer for SOAP-kodet matriser eller SOAP-kodet, flere referanse elementer som datatyper, uansett tilordnes til .NET Framework-samlinger eller nummereringer.

trans-unit.source: As necessary, the collection fix-up method is called during deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Etter behov kalles metoden samlingen rett opp under deserialisering.

trans-unit.source: You should not directly instantiate XmlSerializationCollectionFixupCallback.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke starte XmlSerializationCollectionFixupCallback direkte.

trans-unit.source: SOAP encoding is described in Section 5 of the SOAP 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: SOAP-koding er beskrevet i delen 5 av SOAP 1.1-spesifikasjonen.
